text: Héctor Bienvenido ‘Negro’ Trujillo Molina (April 6, 1908 - October 19, 2002),Social Security Death Index, Hector B. Trujillo, accessed at 20 May 2008 was a general, and political figure. He was the President of the Dominican Republic from 1952 through 1960. He was the brother of Rafael Trujillo. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Presidents of the Dominican Republic Category:Generals
title: Héctor Trujillo
